    "## ðŸŽ¯ Challenge 1: Counting Movies by Genre\n",
    "\n",
    "Let's find out how many movies we have in each genre using GROUP BY and COUNT:\n",
    "```sql\n",
    "SELECT genre, COUNT(*) as movie_count\n",
    "FROM movies\n",
    "GROUP BY genre;\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
