    "\n",
    "We can use other aggregate functions like AVG to find the average rating for each genre:\n",
    "```sql\n",
    "SELECT genre, \n",
    "       COUNT(*) as movie_count,\n",
    "       AVG(rating) as avg_rating\n",
    "FROM movies\n",
